snippet.title: Bullet Bunny - Steam Next Fest 2023 Demo Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is a playable demo for Bullet Bunny, a twin-stick shooter with rogue-like elements, presented for the Steam Next Fest 2023.

Try the demo here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2317880/Bullet_Bunny/

Bullet Bunny (C) penusbmic
